    <string name="settings_about_title">What the app does</string>
    <string name="settings_about_line1">Nexora Player organizes the local audio and video library, plays content with Media3 / ExoPlayer, and supports fast search, playlists, favorites, history, and persistent settings.</string>
    <string name="settings_about_line2">The interface focuses on section-based navigation, compact views, full-screen video playback, and a now-playing style audio screen.</string>
    <string name="settings_about_line3">It also includes album art or thumbnails when available, brightness and volume gestures in video, and options to hide tracks you do not want to see in the main library.</string>

